---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Service Areas | Brainard's Greenscapes Las Cruces, NM"
description: "Brainard's Greenscapes serves Las Cruces, Mesilla, Doña Ana, Anthony, Sunland Park, and communities across southern New Mexico."
---
<section class="py-20">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Service Areas</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">Proudly serving homeowners and businesses across Las Cruces, the Mesilla Valley, and southern Doña Ana County.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      {% for area in serviceAreasSorted %}
      <a href="/service-areas/{{ area.slug }}/" class="block bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:bg-green-100 transition-colors font-heading font-semibold text-green-900">{{ area.name }}, {{ area.state }}</a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% include "partials/banner.njk" %}
